Package simulation.antlr4

Interface SatelliteLangListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
SatelliteLangBaseListener
public interface SatelliteLangListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by SatelliteLangParser.
